{"tid":1436303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實今次比起雨傘嗰陣，已經進步咗好多","createTime":"2019-08-09T09:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T09:49:25.000Z","uid":153600,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2f44f30b30f83756f1809abe1ffb4994fffefb09","tid":1436303,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:14:58.000Z","msg":"今次冇大台，行動都係所有人一齊策劃<br />\n而且識得be water，能攻能守，唔會淨係死佔爛佔，要走嘅時候又會一齊走<br />\n同埋今次有好多後生仔寧願犧牲前途同埋青春，去同呢個政府決一死戰<br />\n社會對勇武嘅接受程度又高咗好多，就算係泛民今次都冇割席冇篤灰<br />\n只要我哋頂得住啲三毛，五毛，中共ge攻擊<br />\n堅持五大訴求同埋冇大台ge原則<br />\n我哋今次就一定贏到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f9d52c3ecd5389d2103c32cc969db8e32d91f9","tid":1436303,"uid":227929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:15:12.000Z","msg":"進步得唔夠"},{"pid":"6cd83e65002a30cc335d1a07719e57ff47d798d6","tid":1436303,"uid":810,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:15:31.000Z","msg":"我地唔係要進步，我地要勝利"},{"pid":"08859a849cc6db83f8937587b1455689312468d1","tid":1436303,"uid":201464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:17:19.000Z","msg":"呢樣先至係正確態度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d7de03786a54d3cf7a5bcaa1c419f03f88d4c1","tid":1436303,"uid":284630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"每星期出黎1-2行動, 動員力同持久力同雨革分別好大<br />\n而且法國同南韓都係成功既例子<br />\n林奠用應付雨革既經驗去出牌, 其實已經輸左"},{"pid":"28e0174c148466374f528fbc5a164523c387ccd6","tid":1436303,"uid":153600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:21:54.000Z","msg":"當然仲係有唔少不足之處<br />\n但係個進步已經好大<br />\n你諗下雨傘嗰陣<br />\n成班左膠喺度唱歌<br />\n又話要乜嘢快樂抗爭，又想贏但又唔肯付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但今次真係見到好多後生仔唔理自己條命，去對抗班警察同政府"},{"pid":"ebeef88d4b079215cf4195c29c1be2337847fe84","tid":1436303,"uid":145496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6cd83e65002a30cc335d1a07719e57ff47d798d6","tid":1436303,"uid":810,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:15:31.000Z","msg":"我地唔係要進步，我地要勝利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:22:07.000Z","msg":"唔進步又點勝利呢？"},{"pid":"b30870d6847afc5bae6649cafc3a762a51e6dfd1","tid":1436303,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12d7de03786a54d3cf7a5bcaa1c419f03f88d4c1","tid":1436303,"uid":284630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"每星期出黎1-2行動, 動員力同持久力同雨革分別好大<br />\n而且法國同南韓都係成功既例子<br />\n林奠用應付雨革既經驗去出牌, 其實已經輸左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:23:33.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n嗰陣日日佔住金鐘<br />\n對班示威者嘅體力消耗都好大<br />\n今次通常用禮拜六日去做示威或者抗爭<br />\n禮拜一至五就休息<br />\n其實個持久力係大好多<br />\n政府亦都更加難諗方法去對付我哋"},{"pid":"1fd285d633798814d26f49fb2e0eac7f19f996d4","tid":1436303,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08859a849cc6db83f8937587b1455689312468d1","tid":1436303,"uid":201464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:17:19.000Z","msg":"呢樣先至係正確態度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:25:26.000Z","msg":"個態度要保持正面<br />\n冷靜理性先至可以為我哋帶嚟勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437b2fb9881132f2a1744122bd231966c0cd262b","tid":1436303,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:27:56.000Z","msg":"當年暴政係用拖延令雨革疲累，同時記者會因持續佔領日日有得開，<br />\n今次係有聚有散，大家都有得充電，黑警記者會唔係日日有新話題。<br />\n但係文宣要加強，香港各項難題直指777暴政，經濟困局都係777一手做成。"},{"pid":"edab11f713cb9c840fb7b4c394cab8cb2538e031","tid":1436303,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:28:21.000Z","msg":"贏唔到都係冇用"},{"pid":"8e31d137ff4ac48976ceffaf3c34031eaf1517a1","tid":1436303,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:30:31.000Z","msg":"呢樣真！我相信可以更加好添！大家繼續努力，同埋一定要記住不割蓆"},{"pid":"1e11184fbf43b4a368368c5ebc6e348fcc0bb2de","tid":1436303,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:35:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13bf515817d723b1a2843ecbf59fd729866058ab","tid":1436303,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:39:05.000Z","msg":"仲有雨傘嗰陣時<br />\n嗰陣泛民嘅思想仍然係比較傳統<br />\n一有少少勇武就立即譴責<br />\n但今次泛民有比較多後生嘅議員，思想比較開明<br />\n佢哋既係和理非，亦都會包容勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b658d355357c81928f0c419ebf19f7cdfe5e4b","tid":1436303,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:46:54.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e16f3e270fd1f4f35d73e9b2a1fa6265fc58b8","tid":1436303,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:48:05.000Z","msg":"因為今次只可以贏"},{"pid":"47e6b5f189af0b05b89a0c6d4dd185b5d6713062","tid":1436303,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08859a849cc6db83f8937587b1455689312468d1","tid":1436303,"uid":201464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:17:19.000Z","msg":"呢樣先至係正確態度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:48:33.000Z","msg":"只要團結,乜都做到"},{"pid":"7fac3df3a416e7c469db1ecf3414e52ece5d3a4a","tid":1436303,"uid":163084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:49:25.000Z","msg":"對準政權！唔再膠化！"}]}